    "function_definition": "CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION public.trigger_analytics_update()\n RETURNS trigger\n LANGUAGE plpgsql\nAS $function$\r\nBEGIN\r\n    -- Schedule a refresh of analytics views (in a real implementation, this would be queued)\r\n    PERFORM pg_notify('analytics_refresh', 'scheduled');\r\n    RETURN NEW;\r\nEND;\r\n$function$\n"
